PrecisOrder (a) authorizing the Canadian National Railway Company to enter into an Agreement with Compagnie internationale financière et industrielle du Québec CIFIQ Inc. which provides for the sale of a seventy percent interest in its Nazareth Street steam plant and distribution system in Montreal, Quebec; (b) designating CCUM and CIFIQ as a "company" for the purposes of this Act; and (c) revoking Order in Council P.C.1988-2281.
